<L>__{exterior rooftop of bree's brownstone night}
<A>__{camera pans from night view of new york city to klute sitting on the rooftop alone as if trying to comprehend all he has seen, the mystery of tom grunemann's disappearance in this world and the mysteries of the behavior of bree. skylight into bree's apartment night alongside of him the skylight of bree's apartment lights up. he looks through the skylight and sees bree enter her apartment. he can hear bree talking to somebody, and then he sees that she is talking to frank ligourin. klute watches through the skylight and hears bits and pieces of the scene between bree and frank. he sees the same kind of symbiosis, the same kind of parody of loving that he saw between arlyn & berger. as the scene becomes more intimate he leaves.}
